== PANDUAN MENJALANKAN CHECKO TODOLIST ==
== VERSI MySQL Lokal ==

PERSIAPAN (sekali saja):
1. Install Go (golang.org/dl)
2. Install Git (git-scm.com)
3. Install XAMPP / MariaDB
4. Clone repo: git clone https://github.com/afdalaziz52/todolist1.git
5. Masuk folder: cd todolist1
6. Download dependency: go mod tidy
7. Import database: buka phpMyAdmin, buat database apk_todolist, import file .sql
8. Isi file .env:
   DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
   DB_PORT=3306
   DB_USER=root
   DB_PASSWORD=
   DB_NAME=apk_todolist
   PORT=8081
   APP_NAME=apk_todolist
   APP_ENV=development
   JWT_SECRET=rahasia_jwt_kamu

MENJALANKAN APP:
1. Pastikan XAMPP/MariaDB sudah jalan
2. Buka terminal di folder project
3. Ketik: go run main.go
4. Buka browser: http://localhost:8081

